lenders.occupational_info:
For more than 20 years, BIG Machinery has been building the world’s leading distributor and supplier of heavy construction and mining equipment.

BIG Machinery stock of heavy equipment, consisting of more than 150 new and used machines. We have the largest fleet in Europe, and consequently, we can deliver the equipment you want at very short notice.

We supply equipment for very varied applications, from mining, construction and road construction to screening and crushing directly from stock: Articulated trucks, rigid frame trucks, back hoes, dozers, excavators, wheel loaders, mobile excavators, graders, generator sets, telehandlers, trailers, trucks, mixertrucks, concrete pumptrucks, asphalt plants and concrete plants.

BIG Machinery delivers heavy equipment of all leading brands as: Caterpillar, Mercedes-Benz, Volvo, Komatsu, Scania and Hitachi.

We are a global company, with locations on almost every continent of the world to serve and support you, and respond quickly to needs.

Money cannot buy equity, or freedom... but if a loan can empower someone to lift themselves up, and boosts their confidence in not only themselves but also humanity, then that $25 is instantly worth so much more.

lenders.name: Jeff
lenders.loan_because: Sometimes, life takes an unexpected turn for the worst & you may not have any idea how to deal with what life deals to you. However, it's important to realize that not everything is the end of the world. Whether the change is major or minor, big or small, forever or temporary, you need to be strong & stand against it. A burden may be something that changes you, but it can also be something that makes you stronger if you allow it to. If you stand up and allow yourself to become a stronger person, then you will. It's important never to let it defeat you. When you allow your will to be strong, there is nothing that can stop you. Friends will help you become stronger in the face of adversity, they will always want the best for you, & will always do their best to make things as good as possible. Some may be able to distract, some may be able to help you adjust, & some may be there for as much moral support as you need. Whatever the case, it's important to allow your friends to help you, & never take your burdens on alone. They will love you for who you are, not what you are or what you cant do. They will cherish your differences, as you cherish theirs. When you change, they will support you. In times of adversity, they will support & adapt with you. Friends will make each day just that much easier.
